      "He founded DFA Records and produced and engineered the album himself in his own studio.",
      "Murphy broke up LCD Soundsystem in 2011 at Madison Square Garden, sold it out in minutes, then reformed the band in 2015.",
      "The 33⅓ book by Sasha Frere-Jones examines how the album works as a midlife crisis made danceable."
