          "Notice the difference between Q-Tip's smooth, melodic delivery and Phife Dawg's more gruff, energetic bars. How do their two styles balance each other?",
          "Pay attention to how the jazz samples are used: unlike many rap producers who chop samples heavily, ATCQ often let them play longer, giving the music a more flowing, organic feel.",
