          "mood": "Menacing, densely layered, unpredictable, darkly funny, intensely focused",
          "mainSounds": "Chopped soul samples looped at slow tempos, kung-fu film dialogue samples, 808 drum machine hits, nine distinct MC voices rotating across tracks",
          "productionStyle": "RZA recorded everything on a sampler with deliberately low fidelity — the gritty, muddy sound was a choice, not a budget limitation. The claustrophobic mix gives the album a sealed, pressurized quality.",
