          "mood": "Intense, intimate, searching, sometimes harrowing, occasionally wry and playful",
          "mainSounds": "Grand piano at the centre of everything, layered vocals, light electric guitar, restrained production that keeps the voice and piano forward",
          "productionStyle": "Produced by Amos and Eric Rosse — the production serves the piano and voice rather than competing with them. Spare where it needs to be, orchestral on key tracks.",
