          "themes": "Includes 'Me and a Gun,' which addresses sexual assault directly and is very powerful but intense. Teacher preview recommended for that track. The album also deals with themes of trauma, religious questioning, and emotional breakdown — handled poetically rather than graphically, but the subject matter is mature throughout.",
