              "hiddenFromStudentView": false,
              "teacherNote": "Promotional single; featured on the Good Will Hunting soundtrack. One of the most famous songs Smith ever wrote — a lullaby from the perspective of alcohol, comforting the listener into staying numb. The seductiveness is the point, and it is deeply unsettling once you hear it that way."
