          "themes": "Explicit sexual content throughout; themes of excess, fame, misogyny, and self-destruction. The album's artwork (painted by George Condo) includes nudity and grotesque imagery that caused widespread controversy on release.",
          "artworkConcern": "The album cover depicts explicit nudity and grotesque fantasy imagery — not appropriate to display without pre-screening. Multiple covers were created; all are provocative. Recommend using text-only fallback or a heavily cropped version.",
