              "teacherNote": "Promotional single. Features Jay-Z, Rick Ross, Nicki Minaj, and Bon Iver. Nicki Minaj's 45-second verse, delivered in multiple character voices, overshadowed everyone else on the track. Rick Ross and Jay-Z both have strong verses — compare all four and discuss what makes Nicki's so striking."
