              "title": "Runaway",
              "displayTitle": "Runaway",
              "duration": "9:08",
              "single": true,
              "explicit": true,
              "hiddenFromStudentView": false,
              "teacherNote": "US #15. The album's centrepiece and its most direct confession. Opens with a single piano note played 35 times before the beat drops. Kanye toasts 'the douchebags' and 'the assholes' — meaning himself. The closing three minutes dissolve into heavily auto-tuned vocal noise, turning confession into abstraction. One of the great album tracks of the 21st century."
