              "teacherNote": "Samples Aphex Twin's 'Avril 14th' — a delicate piano loop that becomes the emotional anchor of a long, meandering meditation on a failed relationship. John Legend provides the hook. The track ends with an extended spoken-word comedy segment by Chris Rock that is extremely explicit and should be noted before playing."
