              "explicit": true,
              "hiddenFromStudentView": false,
              "teacherNote": "Built around a sample from Bon Iver's 'Woods' — Justin Vernon's layered falsetto forms the melodic backbone of the track. One of the most unexpected sonic combinations on the album: indie folk and hip-hop production creating something that sounds like neither."
