              "displayTitle": "Neighbourhood #1 (Tunnels)",
              "duration": "4:46",
              "single": true,
              "explicit": false,
              "hiddenFromStudentView": false,
              "teacherNote": "Promotional single. The album's opening track begins quietly — piano, then Régine's wordless vocalise — before building to a full orchestral surge. The lyric imagines two teenagers tunnelling under a snow-buried neighbourhood to reach each other. The metaphor of escape beneath a frozen, adult world sets the album's emotional theme immediately."
