          "mainSounds": "Synthesizers, drum machines, heavily processed samples (funk, soul, disco), vocoder and voice processing, filtered house bass lines, four-on-the-floor kick drum patterns",
          "productionStyle": "Produced entirely by Bangalter and de Homem-Christo in home studios — hence the title 'Homework.' Raw compared to their later work but full of personality. Sampling is foregrounded rather than hidden.",
