          "mainSounds": "RZA's trademark dark, lo-fi soul samples; haunting piano loops; martial arts film dialogue interludes; GZA's measured, precise delivery",
          "productionStyle": "Sparse and dense at the same time — beats built from obscure samples with heavy reverb and echo, creating the sense of a large, empty space",
