              "single": false,
              "explicit": false,
              "hiddenFromStudentView": false,
              "teacherNote": "A 55-second interlude about Abraham Lincoln's wife, who was institutionalised. The sympathy is entirely with her — 'for very good reasons' is both compassionate and darkly funny."
