              "hiddenFromStudentView": false,
              "teacherNote": "A childhood memory — skating on a frozen lake, a close friendship, a wasp. Stevens has spoken about this song as addressing a same-sex relationship obliquely. One of the album's most emotionally direct tracks underneath its whimsical title."
