    "discussionQuestions": [
        "Gospel music is inseparable from religious faith. Can a listener who isn't religious still be moved by this album — and what does your answer say about how music communicates emotion?",
        "Aretha was one of the most famous pop stars in the world when she made this record. Why do you think she chose to go back to the church at the height of her fame?",
        "The film of these sessions was finished in 1972 but not released until 2018 — the year Aretha died. Why do you think it took 46 years, and does knowing that make the documentary feel different?",
        "This album is a live recording, so you can hear the congregation reacting throughout. Does the audience's response change how you experience Aretha's performance?"
    ],
