        "mood": "Restless, strange, intimate, anthemic, eccentric",
        "mainSounds": "Layered guitars, drums, lo-fi home recordings mixed with lavish studio production, USC Trojan Marching Band on the title track",
        "productionStyle": "Deliberately fragmented — Buckingham recorded many tracks on a home 8-track before bringing them to the professional studio, creating an unpolished, patchwork feel across a 20-track double album.",
