    "keyFacts": [
        "D'Angelo spent five years recording Voodoo and played most of the instruments on the album himself.",
        "The 'Untitled (How Does It Feel)' music video showed D'Angelo nearly nude and attracted so much attention to his physical appearance that he later said it contributed to him abandoning music entirely.",
        "Questlove played drums on the album with a deliberately relaxed time feel — slightly behind the beat — to create a sensation of gravity and physical weight in the groove.",
        "D'Angelo did not release another album for 14 years, returning in December 2014 with Black Messiah."
    ],
