        "mainSounds": "Jangly electric guitars, vocal harmonies, driving drums, piano, clean production with emotional rawness underneath",
        "productionStyle": "Bright and crisp — John Fry's Ardent Studios production is clean and spacious, which makes the emotional content hit harder",
