        "question": "Has something ever been recommended to you as something 'you should have heard by now' — a book, film, show, or song? What did it feel like going in with that expectation?",
        "activity": "Quick write: Name one artist or album that you think is underrated or overlooked right now. Why do you think it hasn't gotten the attention it deserves?"
