        "question": "Has a song ever made you feel two opposite things at the same time — happy and sad, angry and calm, funny and serious? What song, and what made it do that?",
        "activity": "The album was originally going to be called 'Emotional Fascism.' What do you think that title means? Write one sentence explaining what you think it refers to, before you hear a note."
