            "reason": "The album Costello made directly before Armed Forces — also produced by Nick Lowe, also recorded quickly, but slightly rawer and more directly punk-influenced. Comparing the two shows exactly how Costello's ambition escalated in one year.",
            "studentTask": "Listen to 'Pump It Up' and 'Radio Radio' from This Year's Model. How do they sound compared to 'Oliver's Army' and 'Accidents Will Happen'? What changed?"
