        "energy": "Varied — from the driving rockabilly of 'Faith' to the slow, gospel-influenced 'Father Figure'; the album covers more emotional territory than it appears to on first listen",
        "keyIdea": "George Michael proves on Faith that he is not half of a duo but a complete creative artist — and does it by making an album that sounds effortless."
