            "displayTitle": "A Little Soul",
            "duration": "4:14",
            "single": true,
            "explicit": false,
            "hiddenFromStudentView": false,
            "teacherNote": "One of the album's most emotionally direct tracks — a song addressed to an absent father, asking for the minimum: 'give me a little soul.' The orchestration here is warm rather than oppressive, a genuine moment of openness in an otherwise guarded album."
