        "mainSounds": "Distorted and clean electric guitar, bass, drums, Isaac Brock's strained, yelping vocals, occasional keyboards and strings, unconventional time signatures",
        "productionStyle": "Produced by Modest Mouse and Brian Deck at various studios. The sound is dense and layered but not polished — a major-label recording that still sounds like it was made by people who didn't trust the major-label process. The mix gives Brock's voice a slightly desperate, slightly unhinged quality that suits the material.",
