                "artist": "Karlheinz Stockhausen",
                "note": "Irmin Schmidt and Holger Czukay both studied with Stockhausen at the Cologne University of Music — his theories about electronic manipulation, texture as composition, and the dissolution of traditional musical structure are built into Can's DNA.",
