                "artist": "Janelle Monáe",
                "note": "Monáe's approach to conceptual pop albums with a strong personal and political vision — art pop as a vehicle for identity and resilience — descends in part from Björk's model on Homogenic.",
                "manualArtistImageUrl": ""
