                "artist": "St. Vincent",
                "note": "Annie Clark's approach to guitar as an extension of classical training, her theatrical performance style, and her insistence on total creative control are partly shaped by Tori's model of the female artist as composer rather than performer-for-hire.",
                "manualArtistImageUrl": ""
