        "mood": "Sensual, introspective, fluid, warm, mysterious",
        "mainSounds": "Live band soul with organic keys and drums, subtle electronic textures, sparse hip-hop beats, Badu's layered multi-tracked vocals",
        "productionStyle": "Warm and analogue-feeling despite digital production — intimate and unhurried, built around space as much as sound",
        "energy": "Mostly slow and meditative; occasionally builds to emotional peaks but never rushes",
        "keyIdea": "Every song on this album connects to water — as metaphor, as mood, as structure. That hidden architecture is what makes it feel like one thing."
